metadata.name: Coexistence #1
metadata.description:
This is a project developed and inspired by my marble work Medusa which is my tribute to the classical mythological creature.
As a sculptor i make marble work, as an artist i work with all media i find interesting.
My production is about coexistence. Coexistence of different kind of styles and materials, coexistence of digital and analogical, coexistence of the classic and the contemporary.
